{"tid":1239493,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係林鄭記者會幫佢點火 燒埋明日大愚同國歌法","createTime":"2019-06-18T07:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T11:35:57.000Z","uid":79314,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e9621382df5741f84fa10a4a8ef4d00571494398","tid":1239493,"uid":79314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"大家，首先我明白五大訴求一定要問！大家都想佢答<br />\n而林鄭都唔可以再回避<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係，條八婆一定會答完扮喊拎同情分<br />\n我地要拆穿佢！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以我地要燒埋明日大愚同國歌法！<br />\n<br />\n「林鄭請問以你家陣既民望，仲會唔會硬推備受爭議性既 明日大愚同國歌法，從而徹回決定？」<br />\n<br />\n佢答會推，證明佢唔係真心認錯，升級！<br />\n答唔會推，再燒其他惡法！唔好放過佢！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢扮示弱我地就要追打！<br />\n俾大家睇清楚條八婆既真面目！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81ce7bc4b526d49d8638c21104407cf7d86c4bb","tid":1239493,"uid":79314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:43:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"349292d27d52679404c203cfb5cfe6497a029b7f","tid":1239493,"uid":79314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17e51e1818938ca6151c9bca28225a4a5a50a0b","tid":1239493,"uid":79314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:44:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733fbf23440e6629e41881380fec67e73a5ab9f0","tid":1239493,"uid":79314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:45:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490125ab23d79d4df925f719416f109e35ab1516","tid":1239493,"uid":219450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:46:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3edebe84605f9df107d7fb33f2ed393f0d13c5f","tid":1239493,"uid":79314,"like":0,"